span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>audio<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>get_device_info_by_host_api_device_index<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>get<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'maxInputChannels'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Input Device id \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> i<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\" - \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> audio<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>get_device_info_by_host_api_device_index<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>get<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'name'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"List audio devices using python","date":"January 31, 2021","description":"How to list audio devices using python.","author":null}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/python/list-audio-devices-using-python/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/python/streaming-video-using-python/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Streaming video using python","tags":["python"]}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/python/getting-started-moteus-on-mac-using-python/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Getting started moteus on mac usin